<div class="dokuwiki export">



<h2><a name="abs" id="abs">abs</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Składnia:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">int</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>

Funkcja abs() zwraca wartość bezwzględną liczby <em>num</em>. Przykład:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="kw4">int</span> magic_number <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu0">10</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
&nbsp;
    <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Odgadnij magiczna liczbe: &quot;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
    cin <span class="sy0">&gt;&gt;</span> x<span class="sy0">;</span>
    <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Twoja liczba rozni sie o &quot;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span>magic_number <span class="sy0">-</span> x<span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot; od magicznej liczby.&quot;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
C++ dostarcza przeciążone wersje funkcji:

</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">long</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>  <span class="co1">//to samo co labs()</span>
&nbsp;
    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="co1">//poniższe funkcje są identyczne z fabs()</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">float</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">double</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> abs<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
Tematy pokrewne: <a href="fabs" class="wikilink1" title="pl:c:math:fabs">fabs</a>, <a href="labs" class="wikilink1" title="pl:c:math:labs">labs</a>
</p>

